## ?? Support

### Common Questions

**Q: Why is CPU always 0?**
A: Performance counters may be unavailable; system degrades gracefully.

**Q: Why does slow mode show huge time differences?**
A: Thread.Sleep() and screen refreshes are intentional for visualization.

**Q: Can I copy the metrics to clipboard?**
A: Yes! Double-click the metrics label.

**Q: How do I reset metrics?**
A: Programmatic: `PerformanceMonitor.ClearMetrics()`

**Q: How do I get detailed analysis?**
A: `PerformanceMonitor.GetSummaryReport()` generates complete report.

